lso expressed shock over the Telangana rape-murder incident. Punjab govt. is committed to ensure safety of women and so CM will start Punjab Free Police Helpline Number for women to reach home. The state govt. and police are working on more schemes to ensure full-proof security of women.", "008-normal": "Source / Reference Link: https://www.aninews.in/news/national/general-news/punjab-cm-announces-free-police-help-to-drop-women-safely-home-at-night20191203234231/"}}